==English==
===Pronunciation===
*wĕn, /wen/, /wen/
*:'''Homophones''': [[wen]]
*hwĕn, /ʍen/, /Wen/

===Conjunction===
'''when'''
#at what time.
#:''They were told when to sleep''.
#at such time as.
#:''I'm happiest when I'm working''.
#as soon as.
#:''I'll do it when I get the time''.

